Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人把店铺留给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后不知去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里 在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时才会回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很庆幸自己是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论多久都能等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（去横滨买东西了）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}上午2/2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡 有八成都是我在喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的票买好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想直接送你到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还有事赶着去办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你已经帮了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这条路一直走到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想带你去 可我现在要看加油站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 看似就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初濑野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是初濑野阿尔法吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为好久没人叫我的全名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时半会儿楞住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是武藏野快递公司的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快递？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没收到过邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁寄来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看下 是初濑野先生寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 而且还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 究竟是什么呢 不管是什么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是相机吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是相机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让他说明一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有委托方的留言要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 原来有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 直接从这里获取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 直接？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“直接”是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请问你是A7M2型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A7？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 以前我好像是叫这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接获取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是A7M3普及型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 你是机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我来直接传送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不了解其中的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快点来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先牵起手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 舌头让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 请不要一直往后缩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传送过去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人的留言 大致感觉是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暂时还无法回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你敞开心胸 去外面的世界走走看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你而言 十年和一天也许并无区别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信 总有一天你会找到难忘的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了便于你保留那份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难忘的事我也有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 还让你送我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿离车站有十公里呢 难不成你还想走过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要再来我家玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武藏野吗 很远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜心 真是可爱的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我刚去研究所的时候自己取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会取这个名字 我已经忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法你的本名是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“阿尔法”就是我的本名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我们这种“阿尔法型”的很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 大家都叫我“阿尔法”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此就成了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你带来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你知道使用的方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这种机型的话大概没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出附带的这个像奶糖般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 打开后盖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进凹槽里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把盖子盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着把镜头打开 按下这个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一粒可以拍三百张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个镜头的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很像我们的眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像眼球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有连接线吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把细的那端插入盖子上的接口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把另一端的圆球含进嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能看到进入相机视野的画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不太舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算闭上眼睛自己也能看见 很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}下午1/1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了好久 车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了工作以外也能来玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以 随时欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定还会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着她回到陌生的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不免有些寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武藏野之国 那个地方也被称为东都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是邻国 但感觉却很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 抱歉 把你吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那女孩是你朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天她来问过路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和你长得可真像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍贵的景色无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三百张根本不够用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------IN------------
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:18:02.46,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}凝固的夕阳附着的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:10.01,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}将天空晕染成一片红色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:18.53,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}循环的涛声轻轻回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:26.99,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}让人静静地在此凝望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:35.44,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥远的彼方闪耀着的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:43.40,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}点亮在记忆深处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:51.76,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}曾几何时  在那遥远的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------IN------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人送给我的相机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就被我珍藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得应该尽量多拍点才对 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却把它当作宝贝似的随身带着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很轻 携带也很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是手枪套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有点松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天去拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你 很帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拍的风景太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逛逛再说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想请你做我的模特儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像平常那样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待会儿再来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是再往前一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有千百张 先拍一张有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我还蛮小气的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的景色有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.46,0:24:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我只想拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.72,0:24:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天拍了那张就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.50,0:24:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北边的荒地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.86,0:24:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要拍这儿的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.12,0:25:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江之岛的剪影 排列在海面上的街灯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.28,0:25:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.22,0:25:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空仿佛罩上了紫藤色的滤镜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.11,0:26:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.67,0:26:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.69,0:26:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留心就看得入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.76,0:26:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果今天好像是被相机拉着到处转悠
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门时拍下的 一如往常的摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.78,0:26:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我今天所拍的唯一一张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.04,0:26:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.43,0:27:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然感到剩余的张数 也并非那么少了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.18,0:27:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我觉得今天的风景特别鲜明
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.56,0:27:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个瞬间 再次浮现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.05,0:27:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经如同祭典般热闹的世间 慢慢沉静下来的那时
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.96,0:28:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到“时代的黄昏”竟会来得如此悠然闲适
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.62,0:28:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种怡然自得的时光\N之后被称为“风平浪静的傍晚般的时代”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.97,0:28:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我大概会一直注视着这个步入黄昏的世界…
